The paper focuses on evaluating human-computer interaction, which falls under the category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The use of neuroimaging techniques, specifically EEG, is the main focus of the paper, which could fall under Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the importance of data contextualization and objective measures, which could fall under Cybersecurity (cs.CYBER). The paper mentions the assessment of emotions, engagement, flow, and immersion, which could fall under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
